<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10350710>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Seguenzioidea A.E. Verrill, 1884 (Vetigastropoda) from the Calcari a Lucina seep deposits in northern Italy. A–J. The cataegid Cataegis taurocrassa (Sacco, 1895). A–D. Complete specimen from Le Colline (MSF 1230). E–F. Specimen partly embedded in rock matrix (MSF 2351). G–H. Complete specimen from Ca’ Piantè (MSF 2352). I–J. Complete specimen from Ca’ Piantè (MSF 2353). K–L. The calliotropid Calliotropis sp. from Ca’ Piantè (MSF 1076)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10350710/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

